    width_shift_range=0.2,
    height_shift_range=0.2,
   
    shear_range=0.2,
    zoom_range=0.2,
    horizontal_flip=True,
    fill_mode='nearest')
train_set = datagen.flow_from_directory('input/train_resizedvgg net/', class_mode='binary', batch_size=64,  target_size=(160, 160))
# load and iterate validation dataset
test_set = datagen.flow_from_directory('input/test_resizedvgg net/', class_mode='binary', batch_size=1, target_size = (160,160))

In [6]:
def process_image(image_numpy):
    image_tf = tf.convert_to_tensor(image_numpy, np.float32)
    resized_image = tf.image.resize(image_tf,(160,160))
    resized_image /=255
    return resized_image.numpy()
In [8]:
def predictor(image_path, model, top_k = 3):
    im = Image.open(image_path)
    test_image = np.asarray(im)
    processed_image = process_image(test_image)
    
    perfect_image = np.expand_dims(processed_image, axis=0)
    
    predicts = model.predict(perfect_image)
    
    classes = []
    
    prob,labels  = tf.math.top_k(predicts, k = top_k, sorted = True)
    
    prob = prob.numpy()
    prob = prob.squeeze()
    probs = list(prob)
    
    label = labels.numpy()
    label = label.squeeze()
    
    classes = list(label)
#     print("Predictor Classes")
#     print (classes)
#     print (probs)
#     print (class_names[classes[0]])
    return probs,classes
